methods.isResolvable:
Returns true if the resolver can resolve the uri.

:param uri: (java.net.URI) - the uri
:return: (boolean) true if this resolver can resolve uri
methods.resolve:
Resolve uri into an object.

:param uri: (java.net.URI) - the URI
:return: (io.deephaven.engine.table.Table) the object

text:
The csv table resolver is able to resolve CSV for schemes csv+http, http+csv, csv+https,
 https+csv, csv+file, file+csv, and csv into tables.

 
 For example, csv+https://media.githubusercontent.com/media/deephaven/examples/main/Iris/csv/iris.csv.

 
 For more advanced use cases, see CsvTools.
